<h2 class="mcg-sub-heading mcg-mt-md">Instagram</h2>
<p>I post some of the artwork I make here, plus pictures of my dogs. Please <a href="https://www.instagram.com/{{ site.username }}">follow along</a> if you're into those things.</p>
<div class="mcg-mt-sm mcg-feed-grid">
  {% if site.env == "dev" %}
    {% for image in instagramdev.data %}
    <a href="{{ image.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <img src="{{ image.images.thumbnail.url }}" alt="">
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  {% else %}
    {% for image in instagram.data %}
    <a href="{{ image.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <img src="{{ image.images.thumbnail.url }}" alt="">
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  {% endif %}
</div>